rComments: This was Carries first time teaching BMB100B so some of her teaching inadequacies can be attributed to her inexperience. However, she did not make it clear what material was more or less important. Also, she did not effectively communicate with her TAs and the result was utter confusion for the students. She had good intentions, but was not ideal.

This is definitely the best class of the biochem series. Professor Partch is clear, organized, and all of her tests were fair. You will have to study, but you will learn so much in this class. Go to office hours with questions, she's always willing to help!
